            <thetext>qx.xml.Element.getSingleNodeText() use qx.xml.Element.selectSingleNode.
Also, Is it possible to add namespaces param for getSingleNodeText.

From:

    getSingleNodeText : function(element, query)
    {
      var node = this.selectSingleNode(element, query);
      return qx.dom.Node.getText(node);
    }

To

    getSingleNodeText : function(element, query, namespaces)
    {
      var node = this.selectSingleNode(element, query, namespaces);
      return qx.dom.Node.getText(node);
    },

It&#39;s more consistent.

Regards,
Jean-Luc</thetext>
